<h3 id="accessibility">Accessibility</h3>
<p>Most of the ARIA roles and attributes are added and maintained automatically. Set <code>role="tabpanel"</code> on the element(s) that contain a Tab's corresponding content. You should further associate the tab and tabpanel by setting the tabpanel element's <code>aria-labelledby</code> attribute to the tab's id:</p>
<code-sample readonly="readonly">
<template>
  <m-tabs>
    <m-tab id="a">A</m-tab>
    <m-tab id="b">B</m-tab>
  </m-tabs>
  <div role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="a">
    When A tab is selected this should show its content and the ARIA label updated.
  </div>
</template>
</code-sample>
